title: 10 Takeaways from Week 9 + MVP Discussion
itunes:title: 10 Takeaways from Week 9 + MVP Discussion
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis recap Week 9 with their latest takeaways, including: The Chargers found a run game (2:28), don’t count the Steelers out (5:47), Eagles running game is crucial (9:33), Dolphins win the battle…but did they lose the war? (15:12), the Chiefs are more than Mahomes (20:23), Deshaun Watson could be the MVP (23:50), Russell Wilson is clutch (28:29), Raiders have a winning formula with Josh Jacobs (33:50), McCaffrey has all the tools (36:43), and the Ravens dominant win over the Patriots (39:36).
